							"path": ["api", "master-agg-data", "v4", "app", "{{app_id}}", "last-update"]
						},
						"description": "Returns timestamp of last data update for this app.\n\n**Nexus use:** Check before sync — if last_update < previous sync time → skip (no new data)."
