							]
						},
						"description": "Retention: sessions on specific days (not cumulative).\nRetention D7 = unique_users(D7) / conversions.\n\naggregation_type=on_day → only count events ON that day.\nmin_cohort_size=10 → exclude tiny cohorts."
					}
				}
			]
		},
